      <remark>
        <p>
          We will let a <m>\mathbb{P}</m><em>line</em> in the <m>\mathbb{P}</m>SET context to be a collection of 4 cards so that every 3 card subset forms a <m>\mathbb{P}</m>SET.
        </p>
